title: Prek Pnov district
text:
Prek Pnov () is a district ("<a href="Administrative%20divisions%20of%20Cambodia">khan</a>") located in the outskirts of <a href="Phnom%20Penh">Phnom Penh</a>, <a href="Cambodia">Cambodia</a>. It is the largest district by land area.
Administration.
Preaek Pnov is subdivided into 5 "<a href="Administrative%20divisions%20of%20Cambodia">sangkats</a>" and 59 "<a href="Administrative%20divisions%20of%20Cambodia">phums</a>".
